description: Built in 2019 this 2 Bedroom/2 Bath home features an extra room perfect for work or work out from home! Looking for top of the line? The open concept kitchen features Bosch/Thermador appliance package, stunning dark hardwoods floors, Italian cabinets, Quartz countertops, surround sound throughout, custom built ins for ample storage, Bosch ventless washer dryer, deep soaking tub and so much more! A great layout with a kitchen bar and dedicated dining area that flows gracefully from the kitchen into the spacious living room.  Lots of light through many windows. Watch the St Paddy's Parade from your private patio, this fantastic home is just blocks from the beach yet around the corner from all that South Boston has to offer! Over 1200 square feet of living space in this pet friendly building plus extra storage, heated garage parking and an elevator that opens directly into the unit! Just minutes to Downtown Boston by car or The Broadway T Stop.
